  iconImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d496de5628727e245a6fa39db447367d, type: 3}
  description: The God of War franchise is a well known hack and slash game. In terms
    of character growth, the main protagonist, Kratos, has involved across the games.
    In the more recent entries, Kratos being a father now has to take care of his
    child after the death of his wife. Kratos went from a blood thirsty hyper masculine
    character to a character who chose to conceal his brutal past and tries to be
    more emotionally sensitive to care for his child.
